.Sh NAME
.Nm bastille service
.Nd Manage services within jail(s).
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl ax
.Ar TARGET SERVICE ARGS
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
sub-command can manage services in jails.
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl a , -auto
Auto mode. Start/stop jail(s) if required.
.It Fl x , -debug
Enable debug mode.
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Start nginx in myjail:
.Sy bastille service myjail nginx start
.It Stop caddy in myjail:
.Sy bastille service myjail caddy stop
